description:
Hi, (Not all Aussies say G'day Lol) 
I like travelling and camping and eating out and enjoying life. The only thing missing is a special female to share this life with. I love the UK and I would love to meet a female from the UK. My family history is Scottish and English..
I own my own home and I have a good paying job in security. 
I won't go on because I don't want to bore you.. If you would like to know any more about me then please contact me back. 
Have a great day.
